HARD FRISK
Healthy Life Style Approach
HardFrisk is a set of methods and concepts to provide better performance for your athletics. It's more than just another series of procedures and formulas for working-out and prescription for sport related activities. It is somehow like a manipulated life style, a strategy, a different approach! ( kaveh Mofidi - Hard frisk Founder and Designer )
